name: Validate "Final Audit" Transaction on expired policy

testSteps.description: Given underwriter has ability to create policy
* with policy effective date is system date minus 365
* with policy expiry date is system date plus 0
* underwriter creates and books expired policy
When underwriter performs Final Audit transaction on policy with Gross Wages '1000'
Then Total Audited Transaction Premium should be calculated
